          "text": "less likely",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " to want to use and recommend their products.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "In contrast, banks that bake ‘ease of use’ into their banking experience nurture good-will. Even if it means making it easier for users’ to stop using their service.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
